# 🚀 Crewera Reality — Complete Backend API Reference

> **Total APIs: 120+** across 15 modules, covering Public, User, Agent & Admin roles.

---

## Conventions

| Symbol | Meaning |
|--------|---------|
| 🟢 | `GET` |
| 🟡 | `POST` |
| 🔵 | `PUT` / `PATCH` |
| 🔴 | `DELETE` |
| 🔒 | Auth Required |
| 👑 | Admin Only |
| 🏠 | Public (No Auth) |

---

## Module 1: Authentication & Account (10 APIs)

| # | Method | Endpoint | Description |
|---|--------|----------|-------------|
| 1 | 🟡 | `POST /api/auth/register` | Register new user |
| 2 | 🟡 | `POST /api/auth/login` | Login (returns JWT) |
| 3 | 🟡 | `POST /api/auth/logout` | Logout & invalidate token |
| 4 | 🟡 | `POST /api/auth/refresh-token` | Refresh JWT token |
| 5 | 🟡 | `POST /api/auth/forgot-password` | Send password reset email |
| 6 | 🟡 | `POST /api/auth/reset-password` | Reset password with token |
| 7 | 🟡 | `POST /api/auth/verify-email` | Verify email with token |
| 8 | 🟡 | `POST /api/auth/resend-verification` | Resend verification email |
| 9 | 🟡 | `POST /api/auth/change-password` | 🔒 Change current password |
| 10 | 🟢 | `GET /api/auth/me` | 🔒 Get current logged-in user |

