## 🔍 Key Query Parameters (Reusable)

```
# Pagination
?page=1&limit=20

# Sorting
?sort=created_at&order=desc

# Property Filters
?city=Ahmedabad&type=Residential&bhk=3BHK
?price_min=5000000&price_max=15000000
?stage=Under+Construction&status=Active

# Date Ranges
?from=2024-01-01&to=2024-12-31

# Search
?q=search+term
```
